  "text": "The supernatant was incubated with 3xFLAG antibody (Biolegend) and For sequencing, sample libraries were prepared by using the NEBNext ChIP-seq Library (Illumina), according to manufacturer's protocol. Samples were sequenced on NextSeq 500 (Illumina). Bowtie and MACS2 were used for aligning and peak-calling, respectively [CITATION_1] .",
